data.title: Eurovision 2024 Georgia: All 12 songs online
data.meta_description: Eurovision 2024 news: Georgian Public Broadcaster, GPB, has published the songs that will compete to represent Georgia in the forthcoming Eurovision Song Contest. Twelve acts
data.meta_site_name: Eurovision News, Polls and Information by ESCToday
data.text:
Georgian Public Broadcaster, GPB, has published the songs that will compete to represent Georgia in the forthcoming Eurovision Song Contest. Twelve acts will fight to win that right in a national final scheduled for March 1st.

The full list of participants and songs is as follows:

VIVO – Life. Author: Zaza Tsurtsumia

Aleko Berdzenishvili – The beautiful girl. Authors: Mamuka Begashvili, Bibi Kvachadze

Salome Gasviani – Share your love. Authors: Maia Kachkachishvili, Bibi Kvachadze

Irakli Pirtskhalava – Freedom. Author: Irakli Pirtskhalava

Diana Gurtskaya – Peace will come. Authors: Kim Breidenburg, Karem Kavaliani

Salome Korkotashvili – Captaine. Author: Salome Korkotashvili

Teatroni – Georgia invites friends. Author: Kote Malania

Tika Patsatsia – Never change. Authors: Georgio, Giga Kukhianidze

Tako Gachechiladze – Me and my funky. Author: Bibi Kvachadze

Guga Aptsiauri – Don't look at me. Authors: Guga Aptsiauri, George Ergemlidze

Tamta Chelidze – Give me your love. Authors: Maia Kachkachishvili, Christine Imedadze

3G – I'm free. Authors: Avto Badurashvili, Christine Imedadze
